  - m_Id: 27999625216
    m_Localized: '-Press "Start Sound"


      -Drag the slider down until you can
      hardly, if at all, hear the sound


      -Confirm your calibration


      -Only
      move the slider to the left


      -To start over, drag the slider all the
      way back to the right


'
